               <msContents class="#MVM">
                  <summary><p>The first volume of a 2-volume  <title xml:lang="ta">Pākavatam</title>, that is, a Tamil prose version of the <title xml:lang="sa">Bhāgavatapurāṇa</title>. This Tamil version appears to be by <persName xml:lang="ta" role="author">Ciṉṉaiyavāttiyār</persName>, based on the Telugu version by <persName xml:lang="ta" role="author">Timmayyaṉ</persName>.</p>
<p>The second volume is <ref target="https://tst-project.github.io/mss/Indien_0254.xml">BnF Indien 254</ref>.</p>

<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (**** 2023).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p>    </summary>
                  
